text: Michal Jonec (born 30 July 1996) is a Slovak footballer who currently plays for FC Košice as a defender. ==Club career== ===MFK Košice=== Jonec made his Fortuna Liga debut for MFK Košice on 19 May 2015 against ŽP Šport Podbrezová in a 5:0 home victory. He replaced Milan Dimun 59 minutes into the game.KOŠICE VS.
